author: James Wilkinson For Dailymail.Com
title: Enrique Marquez Jr admits helping San Bernardino terrorist | Daily Mail Online
text: BREAKING: San Bernardino attacker's accomplice admits conspiring with gunman to provide material support for terrorism in planned 2011/12 attack on college students and commuters Enrique Marquez Jr pleaded guilty to material aid of terrorists on Tuesday night He bought the assault rifles used by terrorists Syed Farook and Tashfeen Malik He and Farook also planned to attack Riverside Community College in 2011/12 They were also planning to set off bombs on the 91 freeway and shoot drivers Their plan was cancelled when other terrorists were arrested in LA Marquez will get max sentence of 25 years as part of the plea deal Published: 23:57 GMT, 14 February 2017 | Updated: 01:39 GMT, 15 February 2017 39 shares
